Privacy Policy for PomodoroTimer

PomodoroTimer (“we”, “our”, or “us”) respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how our app handles your information.

1. Information Collection

PomodoroTimer does not collect, store, or share any personal or sensitive user data.
We do not collect information such as:
	•	Names or contact information
	•	Location data
	•	Usage behavior
	•	Device identifiers
	•	Photos, media, or other files

2. Data Sharing

Since no data is collected, no data is shared with third parties.

3. Internet Usage

PomodoroTimer does not require an internet connection to function and does not transmit any data externally.

4. Children’s Privacy

PomodoroTimer is safe for all age groups. As no data is collected, it complies with child privacy regulations.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

If any changes are made to this Privacy Policy, they will be posted on this page. Please review this page regularly for any updates.

6. Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
